index-files
———————————

Usage:
	$ index-files slides. --start-from 2 --filter \.png$ --dry-run

Argumets:
	Arguments will be concatinates into file name suffix

Options:
	--help          -h    :    Print help
	--dry-run       -d    :    Do not execute (will print unless quiet)
	--filter        -f    :    Filter filenames to apply (regular expression)
	--prefix        -p    :    Use string as prefix instead of suffix
	--quiet         -q    :    Do not print to terminal
	--start-from    -s    :    Start with this number
	--extension     -e    :    Use this string as extension
